%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arshad%20showers%20praise%20on%20%E2%80%98Ranbir's%20Animal%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701868690000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105788241%2Cimgsize-75244.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Farshad-warsi-shares-a-review-of-ranbir-kapoors-animal-calls-it-insanely-fantastic%2Farticleshow%2F105788249.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105788249.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EArshad%20Warsi%20praises%20'Animal'%20as%20an%20'insanely%20fantastic'%20film%2C%20appreciating%20the%20talent%20of%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20and%20the%20entire%20team.%20Singer%20Adnan%20Sami%20defends%20the%20film%20against%20criticism%2C%20urging%20viewers%20not%20to%20moral%20police%20and%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20classic%20movies.%20'Animal'%20is%20making%20waves%20at%20the%20box%20office.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MPs%20Who%20Quit%20After%20Poll%20Win%20Meet%20PM%2C%20BJP%20Brainstorms%20Over%20Chief%20Ministers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20crucial%20issue%20of%20picking%20Chief%20Ministers%20for%20three%20heartland%20states%20ahead%20of%20next%20year's%20general%20elections%20started%20today%20with%20a%20mega%20meeting%20of%20BJP's%20top%20leaders%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20official%20residence.%20Besides%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20the%20meeting%20is%20being%20attended%20by%2012%20MPs%20who%20resigned%20from%20parliament%20after%20winning%20the%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20session%20is%20the%20second%20consecutive%20meet%20--%20yesterday%20the%20leaders%20had%20been%20in%20in%20a%20four-hour%20huddle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20BJP%20wrested%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20retained%20its%20hold%20on%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20amid%20a%20buzz%20on%20anti-incumbency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20three%20states%2C%20the%20party%20had%20gone%20into%20polls%20without%20a%20Chief%20Ministerial%20candidate%2C%20contesting%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20PM%20Modi%20--%20a%20move%20that%20delivered%20in%20spades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20with%20the%20victory%2C%20the%20knotty%20question%20of%20who%20would%20helm%20the%20states%20has%20come%20up.%20The%20brain-storming%20has%20been%20on%20since%20Sunday%2C%20feeding%20speculation%20about%20a%20hunt%20for%20new%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tallest%20leaders%20of%20the%20states%20--%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Raman%20Singh%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20four-time%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Shivraj%20singh%2C%20while%20being%20in%20the%20running%2C%20have%20left%20the%20decision%20to%20the%20Central%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20these%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20the%20longest%20list%20of%20contenders.%20Besides%20Ms%20Raje%2C%20the%20front-runners%20include%20Union%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20part%20veteran%20Kirori%20Lal%20Meena%20and%20state%20BJP%20chief%20CP%20Joshi.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701868440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fhin51npo_pm-modi-with-leaders-_625x300_06_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmps-who-quit-after-poll-win-meet-pm-bjp-brainstorms-over-chief-ministers-4639536%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20is%20holding%20a%20mega-meeting%20to%20brainstorm%20the%20issue%20of%20new%20Chief%20Ministers%20for%20the%20three%20heartland%20states%20they%20won%20this%20week.%20Besides%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Amit%20Shah%2C%2012%20MPs%20who%20resigned%20to%20contest