ny%20from%20nannies%20about%20where%20the%20children%20have%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20the%20case%20plays%20out%20could%20have%20major%20consequences%20for%20Musk%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20richest%20people%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-grimes-texas-better-california-rich-child-support-fight-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETexas%20limits%20child%20custody%20payouts%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20three%20kids%20to%20%242%2C760%20per%20month%2C%20while%20California%20has%20no%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECourt%20records%20show%20the%20children's%20nannies%20are%20already%20part%20of%20that%20jurisdictional%20fight.%20In%20a%20motion%20filed%20November%2030%20and%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%20this%20week%2C%20Grimes%20accused%20Musk%20of%20limiting%20access%20to%20the%20kids'%20nannies%2C%20whom%20the%20document%20says%20are%20%26quot%3Bbound%20by%20non-disclosure%20agreements%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20required%20them%20to%20sign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20alleges%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrimes-tracked-elon-musk-private-jet-to-serve-custody-papers-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMusk%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20%26quot%3Brefused%20to%20answer%20whether%20he%20would%20relieve%20nannies%20of%20their%20obligations%20under%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20non-disclosure%20agreement%26quot%3B%20if%20Grimes%20%26quot%3Bseeks%20information%20from%20the%20nannies%20which%20likely%20would%20be%20beneficial%20to%20her.%26quot%3B%20It%20also%20said%20Musk%20filed%20a%20motion%20to%20prevent%20Grimes%20from%20getting%20information%20from%20the%20company%20that%20employs%20the%20nannies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20filing%20says%2C%20Musk%20%26quot%3Bwants%20to%20cherry%20pick%20information%20from%20the%20nannies%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20believes%20is%20favorable%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20%26quot%3Bappears%20to%20be%20taking%20the%2