for%20them.%20This%20isn't%20just%20a%20surrogacy%20arrangement%20%E2%80%94%20we're%20family%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20I%20found%20out%20the%20first%20family%20I%20matched%20with%20is%20working%20with%20a%20new%20surrogate.%20She's%20pregnant%20with%20twins.%20We%20still%20have%20the%20type%20of%20relationship%20where%20I%20can%20reach%20out%20and%20check%20in%20with%20the%20intended%20parents.%20I%20want%20them%20to%20know%20that%20I'm%20their%20biggest%20cheerleader.%20I%20hope%20they%20get%20the%20family%20they've%20worked%20so%20hard%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurrogate-miscarried-twice-fired-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701866401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655b852822cf74a5739a1e8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurrogate-miscarried-twice-fired-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20surrogate%20was%20fired%20by%20the%20couple%20who%20hired%20her%20after%20she%20had%202%20miscarriages%20at%206%20weeks.%20She%20delivered%20a%20boy%20for%20a%20gay%20couple%20that%20feels%20like%20family.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurrogate-miscarried-twice-fired-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Sues%20Ex-Husband%20After%20Accusing%20Him%20Of%20Leaving%20Her%20For%20A%20Younger%20Woman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20accountant%20in%20the%20UK%20sued%20her%20ex-Olympian%20husband%20for%20age%20discrimination%20after%20thinking%20he%20left%20her%20for%20a%20younger%20woman%2C%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2023%2F12%2F05%2Fwife-sues-ex-husband-age-discrimination-left-younger-woman-19929332%2F%5C%22%3E%20Metro%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0Eleanor%20Belson%2C%2060%2C%20alleged%20that%20Tim%20Belson%2C%2072%2C%20was%20ageist%20for%20ending%20their%20marriage%20and%20firing%20her%20from%20his%20jewelry%20firm%20where%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20bookkeeper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20British%20couple%20split%20two-and-a-half%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20since%20then%20Ms%20Belson%20has%20brought%20four%20cases%20against%20her%20former%20partner.%C2%A0The%20first%20case%20was%20raised%20in%20April%202022%2C%20where%20she%20claimed%20he%20was%20'ageist'%20in%20ending%20their%20marriage.%20She%20accused%20him%20of%20dating%20a%20younger%20woman%20and%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20taking%20''revenge''%20by%20getting%20rid%20of%20her.%C2%A0The%20couple%20also%20argued%20over%20Thameside%20riverside%20penthouses%20worth%20millions%20of%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20claims%20were%20dismissed%20after%20the%20tribunal%20ruled%20she%20had%20left%20the%20marriage%20and%20Mr%20Belson's%20new%20partner%20was%20older%20than%20her%2C%20at%2063.%20However%2C%20regarding%20her%20claim%20of%20unfair%20dismissal%2C%20the%20employment%20tribunal%20ordered%20Tim%20Belson%20to%20pay%20compensation%20of%20%2411%2C239%20to%20his%20ex-wife%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.express.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2F1776953%2Fwife-sues-husband-age-discrimination%5C%22%3EExpress.co.uk%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20relationship%20began%20to%20sour%20in%202021%20as%20Mr.%20Belson%20alleged%20his%20wife%20went%20on%20holiday%20with%20an%20elderly%20neighbour%20and%20started%20an%20affair%20with%20him.%20Mrs%20Belson%20denied%20the%20allegation%2C%20saying%20the%20neighbour%20aged%2083%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bold%20and%20gay.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Holly%20Stout%2C%20who%20chaired%20the%20panel%20reviewed%20the%20entire%20case%20and%20said%2C%20''Between%20the%20summer%20of%202021%20and%20the%20termination%20of%20the%20%5BMrs.%20Belson's%5D%20employment%20the%20relationship%20between%20%5Bher%5D%20and%20Mr%20Belson%20(in%20all%20its%20respects%3A%20marital%2C%20personal%2C%20and%20work)%20broke%20down%20%E2%80%93%20in%20our%20judgment%2C%20irretrievably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20parties%20conducted%20themselves%20in%20a%20way%20that%20was%20calculated%20or%20likely%20to%20destroy%20the%20relationship%20of%20trust%20and%20confidence%20between%20them%20and%20which%20did%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%20in%20our%20judgment%20destroy%20that%20relationship.%20They%20both%20accused%20each%20other%20of%20lying%20about%20property%20they%20owned%20and%20taking%2Fretaining%20property%20belonging%20to%20the%20other%20and%20they%20both%20contacted%20the%20police%20about%20each%20other's%20conduct.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''They%20have%20been%20unable%20as%20yet%20to%20reach%20an%20amicable%20settlement%20concerning%20their%20divorce%20even%20though%20their%20split%20took%20place%20now%202.5%20years%20ago.%20Mrs.%20Belson%20has%20brought%20not%20only%20these%20legal%20proceedings%20against%20Mr.%20Belson%20but%20also%20has%20brought%20or%20supported%20at%20least%20three%20other%20sets%20of%20legal%20proceedings%20that%20we%20have%20heard%20about%2C''%20the%20judge%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20her%20other%20claims%20of%20age%2C%20disability%2C%20and%20marital%20status%20discrimination%20were%20dismissed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Stout%20said%2C%20''We%20reject%20Mrs%20Belson's%20evidence%20that%20Mr%20Belson%20was%20motivated%20by%20her%20age%20on%20the%20basis%20that%20he%20had%20'left%20her%20for%20a%20younger%20woman.%20We%20accept%20Mr%20Belson's%20evidence%20that%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%2C%20his%20new%20girlfriend%20is%20older%20than%20Mrs%20Belson.%20Further%2C%20it%20was%20Mrs%20Belson%20who%20left%20the%20marital%20relationship.%C2%A0We%20do%20not%20consider%20that%20age%20had%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20it.%C2%A0Whether%20or%20not%20Mr%20Belson's%20new%20girlfriend%20can%20be%20perceived%20as%20younger%20or%20older%20than%20Mrs%20Belson%2C%20this%20is%20not%20as%20we%20see%20it%20a%20case%20of%20Mr%20Belson%20ending%20his%20relationship%20with%20her%20on%20'ageist'%20grounds%20or%20in%20search%20of%20a%20younger%20partner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701866340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fmpojkr1k_court-generic-fourt-files-generic-files-in-court-pixabay_625x300_11_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-sues-ex-husband-for-being-ageist-accuses-him-of-leaving-her-for-a-younger-woman-4639485%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Her%20claims%20were%20dismissed%20after%20the%20tribunal%20ruled%20she%20had%20left%20the%20marriage%20and%20Mr%20Belson's%20new%20partner%20was%20older%20than%20her%2C%20at%2063.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-sues-ex-husband-for-being-ageist-accuses-him-of-leaving-her-for-a-younger-woman-4639485%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-sues-ex-husband-for-being-ageist-accuses-him-of-leaving-her-for-a-younger-woman-4639485%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-sues-ex-husband-for-being-ageist-accuses-him-of-leaving-her-for-a-younger-woman-4639485%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Himanshi%20Khurana%20announces%20break%20up%20with%20Asim%20Riaz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701866316000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105786892%2Cimgsize-863649.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fhimanshi-khurana-announces-break-up-with-asim-riaz-writes-with-due-respect-to-our-respective-religions-we-are-sacrificing-our-love-for-our-different-religious-beliefs%2Farticleshow%2F105786890.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Himansh