%20for%20food%20after%20work%2C%20his%20family%20wrote%20in%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20October%209%2C%20Brown%20visited%20the%20store%20after%20work%20and%20bought%20a%20Panera%20Charged%20Lemonade%20in%20Mango%20Yuzu%20Citrus%20flavor%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20He's%20believed%20to%20have%20spent%20around%2090%20minutes%20in%20the%20restaurant%20and%20have%20drunk%20three%20cups%20of%20the%20lemonade%20in%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20had%20a%20cardiac%20arrest%20walking%20home%20from%20the%20store%2C%20was%20found%20unresponsive%20on%20the%20sidewalk%2C%20and%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20at%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20our%20investigation%20we%20believe%20his%20unfortunate%20passing%20was%20not%20caused%20by%20one%20of%20the%20company's%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20Panera%20said%20in%20a%20media%20statement%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nrn.com%2Fnews%2Fpanera-s-caffeinated-lemonade-blamed-another-death-second-lawsuit-alleges%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENation's%20Restaurant%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20view%20this%20lawsuit%2C%20which%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20same%20law%20firm%20as%20a%20previous%20claim%2C%20to%20be%20equally%20without%20merit.%20Panera%20stands%20firmly%20by%20the%20safety%20of%20our%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20October%2C%20a%20large%2030-fluid-ounce%20portion%20of%20either%20flavor%20of%20the%20charged%20lemonade%20Panera%20offered%20%E2%80%93%20Mango%20Yuzu%20Citrus%20and%20Strawberry%20Lemon%20Mint%20%E2%80%93%20contained%20around%20390%20milligrams%20of%20caffeine.%20The%20chain%20appears%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpanera-charged-lemonade-new-labeling-caffeine-warnings-after-lawsuit-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereformulated%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20beverages%20to%20reduce%20their%20caffeine%20content%20%E2%80%93%20the%20former%20now%20contains%20235%20milligrams%20of%20caffeine%20an