l%20Gandhi's%20ability%20to%20lead%20the%20Congress%20and%20was%20disappointed%20by%20his%20%26quot%3Bfrequent%20disappearing%20acts%26quot%3B%2C%20reveals%20a%20new%20book%20written%20by%20Congress%20veteran%20Pranab%20Mukherjee's%20daughter%20Sharmishtha%20Mukherjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BPranab%20My%20Father%26quot%3B%2C%20Sharmishtha%20Mukherjee%2C%20a%20former%20Congress%20leader%2C%20shares%20her%20father's%20critical%20comments%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20take%20on%20his%20relationship%20with%20the%20Gandhi%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20morning%2C%20during%20Pranab's%20usual%20morning%20walk%20in%20the%20Mughal%20Gardens%20(now%20Amrit%20Udyan)%2C%20Rahul%20came%20to%20see%20him.%20Pranab%20disliked%20any%20interruptions%20during%20his%20morning%20walks%20and%20puja.%20Nevertheless%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20meet%20him.%20It%20turned%20out%20that%20Rahul%20was%20actually%20scheduled%20to%20meet%20Pranab%20later%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20but%20his%20(Rahul's)%20office%20mistakenly%20informed%20him%20that%20the%20meeting%20was%20in%20the%20morning.%20I%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20incident%20from%20one%20of%20the%20ADCs.%20When%20I%20asked%20my%20father%2C%20he%20commented%20sardonically%2C%20'If%20Rahul's%20office%20can't%20differentiate%20between%20'a.m'%20and%20'p.m'%2C%20how%20do%20they%20hope%20to%20run%20the%20PMO%20one%20day%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20features%20pages%20of%20Pranab%20Mukherjee's%20diary%2C%20which%20includes%20his%20thoughts%20and%20ideas%20on%20contemporary%20Indian%20politics.%20The%20former%20President%2C%20who%20died%20in%202020%2C%20worked%20with%20three%20generations%20of%20Gandhis%20and%20held%20top%20ministries%20in%20the%20government%20over%20an%20illustrious%20career%20spanning%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPranab%20Mukherjee%20was%20Finance%20and%20Defence%20Minister%20in%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%20during%20the%20years%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20starting%20his%20political%20journey%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20Amethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20refers%20to%20an%20incident%20that%20left%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20dismayed%20and%20wondering%20about%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20He%20%26quot%3Bwas%20conspicuously%20absent%20during%20the%20flag-raising%20ceremony%20at%20the%20AICC%20on%20the%20party's%20130th%20Foundation%20Day%20on%2028%20December%202014%2C%20barely%20six%20months%20after%20the%20Congress's%20loss%20in%20the%20general%20elections%26quot%3B%2C%20writes%20Sharmishtha%20Mukherjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPranab%20Mukherjee%2C%20according%20to%20his%20daughter%2C%20noted%20in%20his%20diary%2C%20%26quot%3BRahul%20was%20not%20present%20at%20the%20AICC%20function.%20I%20don't%20know%20the%20reason%20but%20many%20such%20incidents%20happened.%20As%20he%20got%20everything%20so%20easily%2C%20he%20doesn't%20value%20it.%20Soniaji%20is%20bent%20upon%20making%20her%20son%20the%20successor%20but%20the%20young%20man's%20lack%20of%20charisma%20and%20political%20understanding%20is%20creating%20a%20problem.%20Can%20he%20revive%20the%20Congress%3F%20Can%20he%20inspire%20people%3F%20I%20don't%20know%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20veteran%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisappointed%20with%20Rahul's%20frequent%20disappearing%20acts%26quot%3B%2C%20writes%20Sharmishtha%20Mukherjee%2C%20especially%20as%20he%20personally%20didn't%20take%20time%20off%20and%20diligently%20attended%20all%20official%20and%20party%20events.%20%26quot%3BHe%20felt%20that%20Rahul's%20frequent%20breaks%20during%20a%20crucial%20period%20of%20the%20party%20were%20causing%20him%20to%20lose%20the%20perception%20battle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20commenting%20on%20her%20father's%20criticism%2C%20Sharmishtha%20Mukherjee%20also%20writes%3A%20%26quot%3BThough%20Pranab%20was%20critical%20of%20Rahul%20and%20seemed%20to%20have%20lost%20faith%20in%20his%20ability%20to%20revive%20the%20Congress%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20undeniable.%20Had%20Pranab%20be