t%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221219%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20photo%20taken%20from%20video%20released%20by%20Russian%20Defense%20Ministry%20Press%20Service%20in%20August%202022%20shows%20a%20Russian%20serviceman%20preparing%20a%20reconnaissance%20drone.%3Cp%3ERussian%20Defense%20Ministry%20Press%20Service%20photo%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERussia%20is%20using%20drones%20to%20kill%20its%20own%20soldiers%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20surrendering%2C%20Ukraine%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20military%20spokesman%20said%20there%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bcases%20when%20Russian%20drones%20have%20killed%20their%20own%20wounded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERussia%20has%20previously%20been%20accused%20of%20using%20deadly%20force%20against%20troops%20retreating%20or%20surrendering.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20forces%20are%20killing%20their%20own%20injured%20soldiers%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20surrendering%20to%20Ukrainian%20troops%2C%20officials%20in%20Ukraine's%20defense%20forces%20and%20military%20intelligence%20service%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20Russians%20do%20not%20allow%20their%20soldiers%20to%20surrender%2C%26quot%3B%20Oleksandr%20Stupun%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20Ukraine's%20Tauride%20Defense%20Forces%2C%20said%20during%20a%20television%20interview%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20even%20been%20cases%20when%20Russian%20drones%20have%20killed%20their%20own%20wounded%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kyivpost.com%2Fpost%2F25078%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Kyiv%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndriy%20Yusov%2C%20a%20representative%20for%20Ukraine's%20military%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20the%20HUR%2C%20told%20the%20Kyiv%20Post%20that%20incidents%20of%20this%20kind%20have%20been%20recorded%20multiple%20times%2C%20including%20in%20footage%20captured%20by%20Ukraine's%20own%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20killed%20its%20own%20soldiers%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20reaction%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20are%20quite%20a%20few%20people%20willing%20to%20surrender%20to%20Ukrainian%20captivity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20using%20deadly%20threats%20and%20tactics%20to%20stop%20its%20troops%20from%20retreating%20or%20surrendering%20since%20it%20launched%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Ukrainian%20unit%20said%20in%20September%20that%20Russian%20troops%20who%20were%20surrendering%20were%20shot%20at%20and%20killed%20by%20their%20own%20artillery%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-opened-fire-on-own-surrendering-soldiers-with-artillery-ukraine-2023-9%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20incident%20they%20filmed%20with%20a%20drone%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWestern%20intelligence%20and%20Russian%20soldiers%20say%20Russia%20is%20also%20using%20barrier%20units%3A%20troops%20that%20stand%20behind%20other%20soldiers%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20withdrawing%2C%20including%20by%20threatening%20to%20shoot%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-likely-new-units-shoot-own-retreating-soliders-uk-mod-2022-11%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20last%20year%20that%20Russia%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20started%20using%20barrier%20troops%20and%20that%20Russian%20generals%20likely%20wanted%20their%20soldiers%20to%20defend%20positions%20in%20Ukraine%20%26quot%3Bto%20the%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20Russian%20soldiers%20said%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20one%20of%20the%20units%20was%20placed%20behind%20them%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Frussian-soldiers-say-blocking-units-placed-behind-them-stop-retreat-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethreatened%20to%20shoot%20them%20if%20they%20did%20not%20move%20forward%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYusov%2C%20from%20Ukraine's%20military%20intelligence%2C%20also%20said%20this%20was%20happening.%20%26quot%3BBarrier%20units%20and%20killing%20their%20own%20soldiers%20is%20what%20the%20Russian%20army%20is%20really%20using%20against%20its%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20reported%20many%20incidents%20of%20Russian%20soldiers%20surrendering%20to%20it%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20invasion%2C%20including%20soldiers%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-soldiers-are-surrendering-to-ukrainian-drones-ukraine-mod-2022-11%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurrendered%20to%20Ukrainian%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussians-offer-armored-vehicles-on-ukraine-surrender-hotline-official-2023-4%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20also%20set%20up%20a%20hotline%20that%20Russian%20soldiers%20can%20call%20if%20they%20want%20to%20surrender%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ukraine%20said%20Russian%20soldiers%20are%20calling%20it%20and%20are%20also%20offering%20to%20give%20equipment%20and%20heavy%20armored%20vehicles%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-forces-kill-own-troops-with-drones-stop-capture-ukraine-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701864507000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657063e958e7c0c29a2a04e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-forces-kill-own-troops-with-drones-stop-capture-ukraine-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20is%20accused%20of%20killing%20its%20soldiers%20who%20try%20to%20surrender.%20Ukrainian%20officials%20now%20say%20it's%20using%20drones%20to%20kill%20wounded%20to%20stop%20it%