y%20ODIs%C2%A0from%20December%2017%2C%20and%20will%20be%20concluded%20by%20a%20two-match%20Test%20series%20from%20December%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20Gill%20will%20also%20be%20donning%20the%20captain's%20hat%20for%20Gujarat%20Titans%20during%20the%20IPL%202024%20after%20their%20regular%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20got%20traded%20to%20Mumbai%20Indians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701864360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fkr8na7bg_brian-lara_625x300_19_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fnot-virat-kohli-or-rohit-sharma-brian-lara-backs-india-batter-to-break-his-test-world-record-4638823%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shubman%20Gill%20scored%20354%20runs%20with%20four%20half-centuries%20to%20his%20name%20during%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fnot-virat-kohli-or-rohit-sharma-brian-lara-backs-india-batter-to-break-his-test-world-record-4638823%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fnot-virat-kohli-or-rohit-sharma-brian-lara-backs-india-batter-to-break-his-test-world-record-4638823%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fnot-virat-kohli-or-rohit-sharma-brian-lara-backs-india-batter-to-break-his-test-world-record-4638823%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20things%20a%20bra%20fitter%20with%2018%20years%20of%20experience%20wishes%20people%20knew%20about%20bras%20and%20their%20bodies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20professional%20fitter%20fitting%20a%20bra.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6569ef8e47f9ecb37d8903aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223658%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBra%20sizing%20is%20the%20worst%20game%20of%20telephone%20ever%2C%20Kimmay%20Caldwell%20told%20Insider.%3Cp%3Eizusek%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20Kimmay%20Caldwell%2C%20a%20bra%20fitter%20with%20more%20than%2018%20years%20of%20experience.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20called%20bra%20sizing%20%26quot%3Bthe%20worst%20game%20of%20telephone%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20told%20BI%20that%20if%20a%20bra%20fits%20well%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20feel%20it%20at%20all.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhurraykimmay.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKimmay%20Caldwell%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20bra%20fitter%20and%20educator%20with%2018%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20underwear%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20worked%20in%20family-run%20boutiques%20and%20for%20high-end%20brands%20like%20La%20Perla%2C%20and%20her%20experience%20comes%20with%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaldwell%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20has%20seen%20thousands%20of%20naked%20bodies%20in%20her%20career%20but%20estimates%2099%25%20of%20clients%20are%20wearing%20the%20wrong%20bra%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20the%20fitting%20room%20with%20her%20clients%2C%20Caldwell%20told%20BI%20she%20learned%20about%20the%20misconceptions%20people%20have%20about%20their%20bras%20and%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20the%20worst%20game%20of%20telephone%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20Caldwell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20things%20she%20says%20people%20should%20know%20about%20buying%20a%20bra%20that's%20right%20for%20their%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBra%20sizes%20can%20keep%20changing%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECaldwell%20says%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20wish%20when%20I%20was%2020%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20breasts%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Caldwell%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20when%20she%20was%20a%20full-time%20bra%20fitter%2C%20her%20most%20common%20client%20age%20group%20was%20people%20in%20their%20mid-50s.%20Caldwell%20attributed%20this%20surge%20to%20clients%20being%20menopausal%20or%20perimenopausal%2C%20which%20she%20said%20is%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fperimenopause-pregnant-late-period-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecond%20puberty%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20means%20breast%20sizes%20can%20drastically%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20hormones%20completely%20change%2C%20and%20our%20bodies%20completely%20change%2C%20and%20no%20one's%20really%20prepared%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Caldwell%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20as%20the%20body%20changes%2C%20breasts%20change%20too%20so%20it's%20likely%20your%20bra%20size%20will%20need%20to%20be%20updated%20regularly%20throughout%20your%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20two%20bras%20fit%20the%20same%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECaldwell%20told%20BI%20that%20depending%20on%20the%20fabric%2C%20fit%2C%20brand%2C%20and%20material%2C%20you%20could%20be%20a%20different%20size%20in%20every%20bra%20style%20you%20try.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20she%20said%20it's%20important%20to%20go%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-bra%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebra%20that%20feels%20good%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20sticking%20to%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20mentality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBras%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20uncomfortable%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20most%20cases%2C%20if%20your%20bra%20fits%20well%2C%20it%20won't%20even%20feel%20like%20you're%20wearing%20a%20bra%2C%26quot%3B%20Caldwell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20BI%20that%20underwire%20bras%20currently%20provide%20the%20most%20popular%20breast%20shape%2C%20but%20their%20widespread%20popularity%20is%20more%20about%20trends%20than%20added%20support.%20She%20added%20that%20in%20the%201950s%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fphotos-how-style-and-shapes-of-bras-evolved-over-time-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20trend%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20for%20a%20pointed%20bust%2C%20and%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20it%20was%20a%20pushed-up%20bust.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBreasts%20did%20not%20change%2C%20how%20we%20shaped%20them%20changed.%20So%20right%20now%2C%20we're%20just%20going%20through%20another%20trend%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere's%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20a%20'normal'%20size%20or%20shape%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20retailers%20are%20increasing%20their%20in-store%20clothing%20ranges%20for%20plus-size%20and%20disabled%20bodies%2C%20they%20are%20still%20lacking%20in%20offering%20the%20same%20options%20in%20lingerie%20departments%2C%20Caldwell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20your%20body%20just%20because%20the%20popular%20stores%20don't%20have%20what%20I%20consider%20popular%20sizes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaldwell%20added%20that%20breasts%20being%20uneven%20is%20common%2C%20likening%20them%20to%20hands%20and%20feet.%20She%20recommended%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebalancedbraco.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Balanced%20Bra%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livilulane.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELivi%20Lu%20Lane%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20stock%20bras%20designed%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECaldwell%20says%20t%3Cstrong%3Ehe%20band%20is%20the%20most%20important%20part%20of%20a%20bra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECaldwell%20also%20described%20the%20mechanics%20of%20bra%20sizing%2C%20and%20offers%20an%20online%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhurraykimmay.com%2Fbrasize%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecourse%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20to%20do%20this%20yourself.%20She%20said%20cup%20size%20is%20relative%20to%20band%20size%2C%20meaning%20a%20D%20cup%20on%20a%2032%20band%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20a%20D%20cup%20on%20a%2034%20band.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20band%20size%20changes%20just%20to%20keep%20that%20same%20cup%20size%20volume%2C%20you%20have%20to%20change%20the%20actual%20letter%2C%26quot%3B%20Caldwell%20told%20BI.%20That%20means%20a%2032C%20is%20the%20same%20volume%20as%20a%2034B%20and%20a%2036A%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20band%20needs%20to%20be%20snug%20like%20a%20hug%20and%20stay%20parallel%20and%20in%20place%20in%20order%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20bra%20to%20do%20its%20job.%20If%20the%20band%20doesn't%20fit%2C%20nothing%20else%20will%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Caldwell%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbra-fitter-things-you-should-know-bras-fit-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701864171000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6569f0bd47f9ecb37d89041a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbra-fitter-things-you-should-know-bras-fit-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bra%20fitter%20Kimmay%20Caldwell%20said%20she's%20seen%20thousands%20of%20naked%20bodies%20in%20her%20career%20and%20estimates%2099%25%20of%20her%20clients%20are%20wearing%20the%20wrong%20fit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22praj%40businessinsider.com%20(Priya%20Raj)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbra-fitter-things-you-should-know-bras-fit-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Pulwama%2C%20a%20Teacher%20Facilitates%20the%20Return%20of%20Migrant%20Workers'%20Bodies%20to%20Their%20Families%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06170500%2Fimage-1580.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPulwama%20(Kashmir)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOn%20October%2030%2C%20a%20migrant%20labourer%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkashmir-pulwama-migrant-labourer-shot-militants-9005663%2F%5C%22%3Eshot%20dead%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20unidentified%20militants%20in%20South%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Pulwama%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%2C%20Mukesh%20Kumar%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20Nowpora%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20took%20place%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Resistance%20Front%20(RTF)%2C%20an%20offshoot%20of%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-cop-attacked-by-terrorists-srinagar-injured-dead-2455276-2023-10-29%5C%22%3Eshot%20at%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20police%20inspector%20while%20he%20was%20off%20duty%20in%20Srinagar.%20He%20was%20grievously%20injured%20and%20was%20admitted%20to%20a%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20such%20a%20volatile%20environment%2C%20Mukesh%2C%20along%20with%2015%20others%2C%20came%20to%20Pulwama%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Purwa%20to%20earn%20a%20better%20wage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20just%20hours%20after%20finishing%20his%20job%2C%20he%20was%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Kumar%2C%20one%20of%20the%2015%20men%20who%20had%20come%20all%20the%20way%20from%20UP%2C%20recalled%20how%20he%20kept%20urging%20Mukesh%20not%20to%20venture%20out%20alone%2C%20even%20if%20it%20meant%20sending%20money%20home.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20wanted%20to%20send%20money%20urgently%20to%20his%20wife%20and%20four%20children.%20His%20desperation%20led%20him%20to%20his%20death%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-eight%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Floksabhaquestions%2Fannex%2F179%2FAU1421.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqals%5C%22%3Emigrant%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20killed%20since%202017%2C%20according%20to%20government%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20identifying%20Mukesh%E2%80%99s%20body%2C%20his%20fellow%20colleagues%20were%20taken%20to%20a%20safe%20house%2C%20where%20they%20wondered%20how%20to%20send%20his%20body%20back%20to%20his%20family%20in%20Purwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20problem%20was%20solved%20when%20Faisal%20Parray%2C%20a%20school%20teacher%20and%20resident%20of%20Pulwama%2C%20stepped%20in%20to%20help%20transport%20Mukesh%E2%80%99s%20body%20back%20to%20Purwa.%20Parray%20also%20assisted%20in%20getting%20the%20body%20embalmed%20to%20ensure%20that%20Mukesh%20would%20be%20received%20by%20his%20family%20in%20an%20undecayed%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202022%2C%20he%20has%20voluntarily%20helped%20facilitate%20the%20return%20of%20at%20least%2020%20migrants%20who%20had%20died%20in%20the%20valley%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20his%20name.%20He%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20part%20of%20the%20police%20or%20the%20army.%20Yet%20he%20helped%20us%20through%20his%20own%20sources%20and%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20how%20painful%20it%20is%2C%20firstly%2C%20to%20lose%20someone%20and%20secondly%2C%20to%20run%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20to%20obtain%20their%20body%20and%20send%20it%20back%20to%20their%20hometown%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Parray%2C%20recalling%20his%20trauma%20of%20losing%20a%20loved%20one%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20he%20had%20helped%20Deepsha%20Dey%2C%20who%20lost%20her%20father%2C%20Pradeep%20Kumar%20Dey%2C%20during%20a%20vacation%20in%20the%20valley.%20The%20road%20accident%20occurred%20on%20May%2025%2C%202023%2C%20on%20NH44%20near%20Awantipora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParray%20facilitated%20the%20local%20transfer%20of%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDey%20also%20credited%20the%20local%20police%20for%20assisting%20her%20at%20every%20step%2C%20even%20when%20the%20death%20certificate%20of%20her%20father%20had%20a%20spelling%20error.%20She%20remembered%20how%20helpful%20the%20locals%20were%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20decided%20to%20donate%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20body%20to%20a%20local%20anatomy%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Nasir%20Raza%20found%20himself%20trapped%20in%20a%20similar%20situation%20when%20his%20cousin%20Zahid%20Ahmed%2C%20a%20labourer%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20road%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2026%2C%20Ahmed%20and%20his%20relative%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20road%20accident%20near%20Pulwama%20while%20being%20transported%20to%20a%20work%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaza%2C%20who%20was%20called%20after%20his%20relatives%20passed%20away%2C%20had%20to%20establish%20the%20identity%20of%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20had%20no%20documents%20linked%20to%20him%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20a%20call%20from%20the%20police%20in%20Kashmir%20that%20my%20brother%20had%20died%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20document%20to%20confirm%20that%20it%20was%2C%20by%20all%20possibilities%2C%20my%20own%20brother.%20With%20this%2C%20Faisal%20%5BParray%5D%20sir%20reached%20out%20to%20me.%20He%20helped%20me%20understand%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20we%20could%20ascertain%20my%20brother%E2%80%99s%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raza%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20that%20for%20two%20days%20after%20the%20deaths%2C%20both%20bodies%20remained%20in%20Kashmir%20because%20their%20identities%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaza%20also%20shared%20how%2C%20at%20his%20own%20expense%2C%20Parray%20sent%20the%20bodies%20of%20Ahmed%20and%20the%20other%20relative%20to%20Delhi.%20He%20also%20arranged%20for%20an%20ambulance%20that%20transported%20Raza%20and%20the%20bodies%20of%20his%20relatives%20from%20the%20airport%20in%20Delhi%20to%20Bareilly.%20From%20there%2C%20they%20took%20a%20vehic