ds%20or%20family%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Witman%20booked%20the%20trip%20in%20April%202022%20and%20paid%20%2432%2C000%20for%20the%20first%20installment%20and%20deposit.%20She%20sold%20her%20four-bedroom%20house%20and%20got%20rid%20of%20many%20of%20her%20possessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20called%20everybody%2C%20I%20kept%20expecting%20someone%20to%20tell%20me%20that%20(this%20was%20a%20bad%20idea)%20and%20I%20called%20my%20financial%20investment%20folks%2C%20and%20they're%20like%2C%20'You%20should%20do%20it.%20Like%2C%20these%20guys%20are%20the%20most%20conservative%20financial%20people%2C%20I%20cannot%20believe%20they're%20telling%20me%20I%20should%20do%20it%2C''%20Ms%20Witman%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%20data-g-r%3D%5C%22lazy%5C%22%20data-gl-method%3D%5C%22loadAnc%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20company%20canceled%20the%20trip%20last%20month%2C%20saying%20it%20could%20not%20secure%20a%20ship%20for%20the%20voyage.%20Investors%20backed%20out%20due%20to%20unrest%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20CNN%20reported.%20The%20company%20said%20they%20are%20''actively%20working%20on%20creating%20alternative%20plans%20for%20the%20future.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I've%20been%20working%20over%20the%20last%20eight%20months%20to%20get%20everything%20in%20line%2C%20my%20life%20organized%2C%20so%20that%20I%20can%20make%20it%20happen.%20It%20was%20disappointing%20to%20find%20out%20it%20wasn't%20going%20to%20pan%20out%2C''%20Ms%20Witman%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cincinnati.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2F27%2Fkeri-witman-sold-home-board-canceled-three-year-life-at-sea-cruise%2F71717678007%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1d9qPBeBlT3Yr9UagBKkgUd48aR15LLK5iWF9tHXmtZRhiRD2O4CAqO30%5C%22%3EThe%20Enquirer.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20possessions%20that%20were%20meant%20to%20be%20on%20the%20cruise%20are%20now%20in%20storage%2C%20and%20she%20is%20living%20in%20a%20rented%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%