ss%20will%20have%20to%20necessarily%20concede%20ground%20to%20the%20other%20partners%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20To%20begin%20with%2C%20the%20convenorship%20of%20INDIA%20should%20be%20formalised%20in%20favour%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20or%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20or%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20The%20romantic%20notion%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cchairperson%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20non-BJP%20alliance%20is%20today%20stranded%20in%20irrelevance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20extent%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20remains%20crucial%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20must%20learn%20to%20accept%20that%20%E2%80%9CUP%20is%20not%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20kingdom.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20imperative%20for%20Priyanka%20to%20internalise%20the%20fact%20that%20UP%2C%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20has%20moved%20on%20and%20is%20no%20longer%20enamoured%20of%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20and%20sacrifices.%20And%2C%20if%20she%20has%20even%20an%20iota%20of%20familiarity%20with%20reality%2C%20she%20should%20be%20prepared%20to%20work%20to%20bring%20Mayawati%20into%20conversation%20and%20devise%20a%20modus%20vivendi%20between%20her%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20On%20its%20part%2C%20the%20Congress%20does%20not%20deserve%20more%20than%20two%20seats%20in%20any%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20in%20the%20state.%20Her%20challenge%20is%20to%20do%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20deny%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20the%20Modi-Yogi%20brand.%20This%20means%20that%20for%20now%20she%20will%20need%20to%20prioritise%20a%20change%20of%20regime%20in%20New%20Delhi%20over%20and%20above%20her%20personal%20quest%20for%20glory%20and%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20the%20Congress%20vote%20share%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20is%20nothing%20to%20snigger%20at.%20And%20that%20is%20all%20the%20more%20reason%20for%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20to%20recognise%20how%20to%20play%20the%20game%20differently%20if%20it%20at%20all%20