n%20points%20outside%20shelters%20and%20deliver%20food%20in%20places%20that%20had%20been%20impossible%20to%20reach%2C%20including%20in%20some%20northern%20areas.%20WFP%20reached%20approximately%20250%2C000%20people%20in%20just%20one%20week%2C%E2%80%9D%20its%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTragically%2C%20this%20desperately%20needed%20progress%20is%20now%20being%20lost.%20The%20renewed%20fighting%20makes%20the%20distribution%20of%20aid%20almost%20impossible%20and%20endangers%20the%20lives%20of%20humanitarian%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbove%20all%2C%20it%20is%20a%20disaster%20for%20the%20civilian%20population%20of%20Gaza%2C%20more%20than%202%20million%20people%2C%20whose%20only%20lifeline%20is%20food%20assistance%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20WFP%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20reiterated%20the%20need%20for%20humanitarian%20workers%20to%20have%20safe%20and%20uninterrupted%20access%20to%20the%20Gaza%20strip%20and%20urged%20for%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20as%20well%20as%20for%20all%20leaders%20to%20work%20toward%20a%20political%20solution%20that%20would%20%E2%80%9Cend%20the%20suffering%20of%20families%20on%20all%20sides%20of%20this%20harrowing%20conflict%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20is%20reproduced%20in%20full%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFood%20security%20issues%20are%20not%20new%20to%20the%20beleaguered%20Palestinian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freliefweb.int%2Freport%2Foccupied-palestinian-territory%2Ffrance-supports-unrwa-emergency-food-assistance-programme-gaza-enar%5C%22%3EThree%20out%20of%20four%20Gazans%20relied%20on%20emergency%20food%20assistance%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20of%20January%20this%20year%2C%20well%20before%20hostilities%20began%20on%20October%207%2C%20the%20WFP%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20has%20made%20things%20worse%20and%20the%20WFP%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F11%2F30%2Fgaza-hunger-food-aid-unwra%2F%5C%22%3Erisk%20of%20starvation%20remained%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20during%20the%20precious%20seven-day%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20media%20office%2C%2016%2C248%20people%2C%20including%207%2C112%20children%20and%204%2C885%20women%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20by%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20between%20October%207%20and%20Tuesday%20(December%206)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsouthern-gaza-israel-mounts-fiercest-attacks-so-far-war-against-hamas-2023-12-06%2F%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20health%20ministry%20was%20yet%20to%20verify%20the%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20military%20has%20begun%20an%20offensive%20in%20southern%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20main%20city%2C%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20describing%20Tuesday%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20intense%20day%E2%80%9D%20since%20it%20began%20ground%20operations%2C%20Reuters%20quoted%20an%20Israeli%20military%20commander%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-palestine-war-benjamin-netanyahu-captain-america-problem%5C%22%3EIsrael-Palestine%20War%3A%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20Captain%20America%20Problem%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStatement%20by%20the%20World%20Food%20Programme%20on%20growing%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EROME%20%E2%80%93%20The%20resumption%20of%20hostilities%20in%20Gaza%20will%20only%20intensify%20the%20catastrophic%20hunger%20crisis%20that%20already%20threatens%20to%20overwhelm%20the%20civilian%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seven-day%20pause%20in%20fighting%20allowed%20the%20United%20Nations%20World%20Food%20Programme%20(WFP)%20and%20our%20partners%20some%20safety%20to%20scale%20up%20relief%20operations.%20In%20that%20time%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20double%20the%20number%20of%20distribution%20points%20outside%20shelters%20and%20deliver%20food%20in%20places%20that%20had%20been%20impossible%20to%20reach%2C%20including%20in%20some%20northern%20areas.%20WFP%20reached%20approximately%20250%2C000%20people%20in%20just%20one%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETragically%2C%20this%20desperately%20needed%20progress%20is%20now%20being%20lost.%20The%20renewed%20fighting%20makes%20the%20distribution%20of%20aid%20almost%20impossible%20and%20endangers%20the%20lives%20of%20humanitarian%20workers.%20Above%20all%2C%20it%20is%20a%20disaster%20for%20the%20civilian%20population%20of%20Gaza%2C%20more%20than%202%20million%20people%2C%20whose%20only%20lifeline%20is%20food%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHumanitarians%20must%20have%20safe%2C%20unimpeded%2C%20and%20sustained%20access%2C%20so%20we%20are%20able%20to%20distribute%20life-saving%20assistance%20throughout%20the%20territory.%20All%20parties%20must%20uphold%20their%20obligations%20under%20international%20humanitarian%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20only%20a%20lasting%20peace%20can%20end%20the%20suffering%20and%20avert%20the%20looming%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%20in%20Gaza.%20WFP%20calls%20for%20a%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20and%20urges%20all%20leaders%20to%20work%20with%20the%20utmost%20urgency%20to%20find%20political%20solutions%20that%20can%20end%20the%20suffering%20of%20families%20on%20all%20sides%20of%20this%20harrowing%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%23%20%23%20%23%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20World%20Food%20Programme%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20humanitarian%20organization%20saving%20lives%20in%20emergencies%20and%20using%20food%20assistance%20to%20build%20a%20pathway%20to%20peace%2C%20stability%20and%20prosperity%20for%20people%20recovering%20from%20conflict%2C%20disasters%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701855042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%