2%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F29142658%2F5606166528_b12b9c251a_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Delhi%20high%20court%20on%20Tuesday%20(December%205)%20asked%20the%20Union%20to%20respond%20to%20a%20plea%20by%20the%20mother%20of%20a%2034-year-old%20nurse%20from%20Kerala%20facing%20death%20sentence%20in%20Yemen%20for%20murdering%20a%20Yemeni%20national.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENimisha%20Priya%20was%20convicted%20for%20murdering%20Talal%20Abdo%20Mahdi%2C%20who%20died%20in%20July%202017%2C%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fdelhi%2Fdelhi-hc-asks-centre-to-reply-to-womans-plea-to-facilitate-travel-to-yemen-to-save-daughter-on-death-row-2794261%5C%22%3Eshe%20allegedly%20injected%20him%20with%20sedatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20back%20her%20passport%20from%20his%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2013%2C%202023%2C%20the%20top%20court%20in%20Yemen%20rejected%20Priya%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20and%20ordered%20her%20execution.%20However%2C%20as%20Yemen%20follows%20Sharia%20law%2C%20she%20is%20eligible%20to%20s%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67544059%5C%22%3Eecure%20a%20pardon%20from%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20family%20by%20paying%20%3Cem%3Ediyah%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20%E2%80%9Cblood%20money%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriya%E2%80%99s%20mother%20had%20moved%20the%20high%20court%20earlier%20this%20year%20earlier%20to%20seek%20permission%20to%20travel%20to%20Priya%20as%20Yemen%20has%20placed%20a%20travel%20ban%20on%20Indian%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Subhash%20Chandran%20K.R.%2C%20who%20is%20representing%20Priya%E2%80%99s%20mother%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fdelhi%2Fdelhi-hc-asks-centre-to-reply-to-womans-plea-to-facilitate-travel-to-yemen-to-save-daughter-on-death-row-2794261%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20petitioner%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20asking%20the%20government%20to%20pay%20the%20blood%20money%20and%20was%20only%20seeking%20permission%20to%20travel%20to%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20high%20court%20last%20week%20rejected%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20a%20lobby%20group%20called%20Save%20Nimisha%20Priya%20International%20Action%20Council%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20India%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20diplomatic%20presence%20in%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20advised%20that%20please%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20there%20because%20it%20will%20not%20be%20possible%20for%20us%20to%20provide%20any%20service.%20There%20is%20no%20single%20Indian%20there%20to%20help%20you%20or%20to%20provide%20security%20to%20you.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20people%20to%20go%20there%20or%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20hostile%20position.%20There%20is%20no%20consular%20officer%20there%20or%20even%20connection%20with%20the%20current%20government%20in%20Yemen%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Union%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20said%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20assessment%20is%20based%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67544059%5C%22%3Epolitical%20condition%20in%20Yemen%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20has%20been%20caught%20in%20a%20civil%20war%20between%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20official%20government%20and%20Houthi%20rebels%20since%202014.%20Since%20India%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20recognise%20Houthis%2C%20a%20trip%20to%20Yemen%20is%20unsafe%20for%20Indian%20nationals.%20The%20Union%20also%20clarified%20in%20court%20that%20there%20are%20no%20direct%20flights%20operating%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lobby%20group%20had%20approached%20the%20high%20court%20last%20year%20and%20sought%20direction%20to%20the%20Union%20to%20%E2%80%98facilitate%20diplomatic%20interventions%20as%20well%20as%20negotiations%20with%20the%20family%20of%20the%20victim%20on%20behalf%20of%20Nimisha%20Priya%20to%20save%20her%20life%20by%20paying%20blood%20money%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%20in%20a%20time-bound%20manner%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fdelhi%2Fdelhi-hc-asks-centre-to-reply-to-womans-plea-to-facilitate-travel-to-yemen-to-save-daughter-on-death-row-2794261%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20said%20that%20Mahdi%20had%20forged%20documents%20to%20show%20that%20Priya%20was%20his%20wife%20to%20abuse%20and%20torture%20her.%20It%20also%20accuses%20Mahdi%20of%20taking%20away%20Priya%E2%80%99s%20passport%20and%20all%20of%20the%20revenue%20from%20the%20clinic%20that%20the%20two%20ran%20in%20partnership.When%20Priya%20approached%20Yemeni%20police%2C%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67544059%5C%22%3Eallegedly%20locked%20her%20up%20for%20six%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20taking%20action%20against%20Mahdi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepa%20Joseph%2C%20lawyer%20and%20social%20activist%20and%20vice-chair%20of%20the%20Save%20Nimisha%20council%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67544059%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20BBC%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20support%20is%20key%20to%20saving%20Nimisha.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20option%20is%20to%20seek%20forgiveness%20from%20Mahdi%E2%80%99s%20family%20and%20negotiate%20blood%20money%20with%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20earlier%20refused%20to%20direct%20the%20Union%20to%20negotiate%20payment%20of%20blood%20money%20to%20save%20Priya%E2%80%99s%20life%20but%20asked%20it%20to%20pursue%20legal%20remedies%20against%20her%20conviction%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701850165000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F29142658%2F5606166528_b12b9c251a_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID