nion%20government%20told%20the%20parliament%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20December%205%2C%20that%20it%20is%20ready%20to%20hold%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20it%20is%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20announce%20the%20schedule%20whenever%20it%20feels%20appropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20ready%20for%20elections%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20ask%20the%20EC%20for%20it%20as%20it%20is%20an%20independent%20constitutional%20body%20and%20only%20it%20can%20decide%20when%20to%20hold%20polls%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jitendra%20Singh%2C%20a%20junior%20minister%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20(PMO)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fready-for-jk-polls-up-to-ec-to-decide-on-date-government-in-lok-sabha%2Farticleshow%2F105763889.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20told%20the%20parliament%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20ensured%20that%20the%20country%20has%20just%20one%20flag%20and%20one%20constitution%20as%20opposition%20members%20clashed%20with%20treasury%20benches%20over%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%E2%80%99s%20remark%20was%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reservation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20and%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reorganisation%20(Amendment)%20Bill.%20He%20countered%20Trinamool%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20(TMC)%20Saugata%20Roy%20who%20had%20said%20%E2%80%9Cone%20flag%2C%20one%20prime%20minister%2C%20one%20constitution%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20political%20slogan%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Shah%20wondered%20how%20a%20country%20could%20have%20two%20prime%20ministers%2C%20two%20constitutions%2C%20and%20two%20flags.%20He%20added%20that%20it%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20political%20slogan%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20his%20party%20firmly%20believes%20in%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhosoever%20did%20it%20was%20wrong.%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20corrected%20it.%20Your%20approval%20or%20disagreement%20does%20not%20matter.%20The%20entire%20country%20wanted%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20countered%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20questioned%20the%20government%20over%20introducing%20amendments%20to%20the%20Bill%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20yet%20to%20deliver%20its%20verdict%20on%20the%20Article%20370%20case.%20The%20apex%20court%20concluded%2016%20days%20of%20hearings%20in%20the%20case%20in%20September.%20The%20court%20is%20expected%20to%20pronounce%20its%20verdict%20sometime%20this%20month.%20Article%20370%20gave%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20the%20power%20to%20have%20a%20separate%20constitution%2C%20a%20state%20flag%2C%20and%20autonomy%20of%20internal%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20National%20Conference%20MP%20Hasnain%20Masoodi%20sought%20to%20know%20from%20the%20government%20why%20did%20it%20not%20conduct%20elections%20if%20felt%20the%20situation%20was%20peaceful%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20He%20alleged%20that%20no%20attempt%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20restore%20statehood%20as%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20legislature%20in%202018%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20has%20been%20under%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%2C%20prompting%20local%20political%20parties%20to%20demand%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20resume%20electoral%20activities%20in%20the%20Union%20territory.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20official%20statements%2C%20the%20delay%20is%20due%20to%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20(BJP)%E2%80%99s%20local%20unit%20wanting%20to%20defer%20the%20exercise%20at%20least%20till%20the%202024%20parliamentary%20polls%2C%20as%20it%20is%20not%20yet%20ready%20to%20face%20any%20polls%20even%20local%20body%20polls%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20previous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flet-al