rl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbus-plunges-into-a-ravine-killing-16-in-the-philippines-13023874%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbus-plunges-into-a-ravine-killing-16-in-the-philippines-13023874%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Some%20Things%20Better%20Left%20Unsaid'%3A%20Justice%20Kaul%20on%20Why%20Judges'%20Appointment%20Delays%20Matter%20Unlisted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EJustice%20S.K.%20Kaul%20on%20Tuesday%20(December%205)%20said%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20he%20did%20not%20know%20why%20a%20petition%20challenging%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20delay%20in%20appointing%20judges%20whose%20name%20had%20been%20cleared%20by%20the%20Collegium%20was%20not%20being%20listed%20in%20front%20of%20him%20that%20day%2C%20despite%20it%20earlier%20being%20decided%20that%20it%20would%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%20said%20he%20had%20not%20deleted%20the%20matter%20from%20the%20cause%20list%2C%20nor%20was%20he%20unwilling%20to%20hear%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Kaul%20and%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20was%20informed%20by%20advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20that%20the%20case%20had%20been%20deleted%20without%20any%20notice.%20Bhushan%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20strange%20that%20it%20is%20deleted%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20added%20that%20the%20bench%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20ask%20for%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20registry%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20not%20deleted%20it%20or%20expressed%20unwillingness%20to%20take%20it%20up.%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20CJI%20is%20aware%20of%20it%20(the%20deletion).%20Some%20things%20are%20best%20left%20unsaid.%20We%20will%20see%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Kaul%20responded%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fi-did-not-delete-justice-sk-kaul-deletion-judges-appointments-case-from-cause-list%5C%22%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20was%20hearing%20two%20petitions%20including%20one%20by%20the%20Bengaluru%20Advocates%20Association%20seeking%20contempt%20of%20court%20proceedings%20against%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20allegedly%20delaying%20clearing%20the%20names%20proposed%20by%20the%20Collegium.%20Justice%20Kaul%2C%20who%20is%20himself%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Collegium%2C%20had%20last%20heard%20the%20matter%20on%20November%2020%20and%20then%20posted%20it%20for%20December%205.%20He%20is%20set%20to%20retire%20on%20December%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20last%20heard%20the%20matter%2C%20Justice%20Kaul%20had%20expressed%20displeasure%20over%20what%20he%20called%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cpick%20and%20choose%E2%80%9D%20attitude.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9COf%20the%20names%20recommended%20for%20appointment%20as%20HC%20judges%20recently%2C%20eight%20have%20not%20been%20cleared%2C%20including%20some%20who%20are%20senior%20to%20those%20who%20have%20been%20appointed.%20Besides%2C%20five%20names%20from%20the%20earlier%20lot%20which%20were%20reiterated%2C%20too%2C%20have%20not%20been%20appointed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20added%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsome-things-best-left-unsaid-sc-on-petitions-not-listed-for-hearing-9056132%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20has%20troubled%20us%20is%20this.%20Even%20now%2C%20the%20last%20lot%20of%20names%2C%20we%20considered%20the%20opinions%20of%20the%20government%2C%20took%20into%20account%20all%20the%20material%2C%20(but)%20not%20even%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20names%20are%20cleared.%20Out%20of%20that%20also%2C%20when%20you%20detain%20eight%20names%2C%20it%20upsets%20the%20seniority%2C%20and%20sends%20a%20very%20wrong%20signal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701839329000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsome-things-better-left-unsaid-justice-kaul-on-why-judges-appointment-delays-matter-unlisted%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20matter%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20heard%20by%20the%20Justice%20Kaul%20bench%20on%20Tuesday%20but%20was%20deleted.%20The%20judge%20made%20clear%20that%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20deletion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsome-things-better-left-unsaid-justice-kaul-on-why-judges-appointment-delays-matter-unlisted%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Babri%20Masjid%20Demolition%20Inalterably%20Changed%20the%20Trajectory%20of%20India's%20History%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fbabri-masjid-demolition.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20on%20December%206%2C%201992%20was%20that%20seminal%20moment%20in%20our%20national%20life%20that%20inalterably%20changed%20the%20trajectory%20of%20our%20history.%20From%20that%20day%20on%2C%20secular%20India%20was%20up%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20I%20write%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20swept%20the%20%E2%80%9Csemi-final%E2%80%9D%20assembly%20polls%2C%20winning%20convincingly%20in%20three%20of%20the%20four%20major%20states%20(not%20including%20Mizoram%2C%20which%2C%20like%20the%20other%20northeastern%20states%2C%20is%20treated%20as%20an%20appendage%20of%20the%20Union.%20Who%20cares%20what%20happens%20there!).%20And%20our%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20the%20shining%20star%20of%20Hindutva%20%E2%80%93%20has%20triumphed%20again%2C%20crushing%20all%20in%20his%20wake.%20His%20gloating%20victory%20speech%20predicted%20an%20inevitable%20hat-trick%20of%20wins%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%202024%20and%20ended%20with%20this%20Caesar-like%20brag%3A%20%E2%80%9CModi%E2%80%99s%20(third%20person%2C%20singular)%20guarantee%20begins%20when%20hopes%20from%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20promises%20end.%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20is%20truly%20unstoppable!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irresistible%20saffron%20imprint%20on%20the%20body%20politic%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20December%206%2C%201992%2C%20that%20dark%20day%20when%20the%20Hindutva%20project%20was%20kick-started%20with%20a%20brutal%20transgression%20of%20the%20law.%20Cocking%20a%20snook%20at%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekar%20sevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20their%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20handlers%20%E2%80%93%20with%20a%20knowing%20wink%20from%20the%20law-enforcers%20%E2%80%93%20brought%20down%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%20This%20heinous%20act%20of%20desecration%20was%20greeted%20by%20a%20large%20section%20of%20people%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20wild%20excitement%20seen%20when%20India%20beats%20Pakistan%20in%20cricket.%20The%20joyous%20response%20was%20not%20restricted%20to%20the%20lumpen%20elements%20who%20brought%20down%20the%20Masjid%20but%20was%20pervasive%20across%20the%20country%2C%20even%20among%20denizens%20in%20boardrooms%20and%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20more%20profound%20level%2C%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20was%20a%20frontal%20assault%20on%20our%20collective%20identity%20as%20a%20secular%20nation.%20More%20than%20anything%20else%2C%20it%20demonstrated%20the%20power%20of%20the%20ethnocentric%20Hindutva%20ideology%20that%20upholds%20the%20supremacy%20of%20Hindus%20and%20purveys%20a%20pathological%20animosity%20toward%20Muslims%20and%20Christians.%20This%20doctrine%20of%20Hindu%20exclusiveness%20has%20become%20a%20more%20than%20formidable%20alternative%20to%20the%20secular%20principle%20of%20pluralism%20and%20inclusion%20enunciated%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20It%20has%20stimulated%20a%20second%20partition%20of%20the%20country%2C%20albeit%20metaphorical%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20it%20is%20not%20a%20physical%20territorial%20split%20but%20a%20schismatic%20division%20of%20minds%20based%20on%20religion.%20From%20the%20day%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20destruction%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20credo%20of%20majoritarian%20nationalism%20has%20been%20in%20deadly%20political%20and%20social%20combat%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20envisaged%20by%20our%20founding%20fathers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Thirty-One%20Years%20After%20Babri%20Demolition%2C%20an%20Important%20Reminder%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbabri-demolition-anniversary-doctrine-non-retrogression%5C%22%3EThirty-One%20Years%20After%20Babri%20Demolition%2C%20an%20Important%20Reminder%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20before%20his%20death%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20assessed%20the%20threat%20to%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20security%20thus%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20danger%20to%20India%2C%20mark%20you%2C%20is%20not%20communism.%20It%20is%20Hindu%20right-wing%20communalism.%E2%80%9D%20How%20prophetic%20have%20been%20his%20words!%20While%20it%20is%20true%20that%20the%20communalism%20of%20one%20group%20feeds%20on%20the%20communalism%20of%20the%20other%2C%20it%20is%20undeniable%20that%20only%20majority%20communalism%20has%20the%20power%20to%20alter%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20Indian%20polity%20by%20subverting%20the%20basic%20principles%20of%20democracy%20and%20secularism.%20His%20warnings%20have%20gone%20unheeded%20and%20today%20the%20country%20is%20on%20the%20brink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20Independence%2C%20the%20citizens%20of%20India%2C%20mainly%20Hindu%2C%20had%20outright%20rejected%20the%20communal%20for%20the%20secular.%20The%20values%20that%20embellish%20the%20Preamble%20of%20our%20Constitution%20were%20quite%20simply%20the%20will%20of%20the%20majority.%20This%20was%20the%20ideal%20that%20the%20country%20aspired%20for%20but%20given%20the%20trauma%20of%20Partition%20and%20the%20historical%20animosity%20between%20the%20two%20communities%2C%20it%20was%20always%20going%20to%20be%20a%20hazardous%20project.%20Even%20as%20the%20nation%20wrestled%20with%20the%20problems%20of%20hunger%2C%20disease%20and%20unemployment%2C%20the%20fundamentalist%20forces%2C%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%2C%20were%20engaged%20in%20stymieing%20all%20attempts%20at%20cultural%20syncretism%20between%20the%20communities.%20Tragically%2C%20they%20have%20had%20unmitigated%20success%20in%20polarising%20our%20society%20on%20communal%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trishul-waving%20kar%20sevaks%20atop%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20dome%20represented%20a%20deviant%20religious%20militancy%20that%20undermined%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20core%20values.%20It%20diminished%20the%20land%20of%20Buddha%20and%20Gandhi%20that%20was%20tolerant%20of%20all%20religions%20and%20transformed%20it%20into%20a%20deeply%20polarised%2C%20violent%20majoritarian%20state.%20At%20the%20ideological%20plane%2C%20the%20cultural%20eclecticism%20that%20marked%20the%20world%20view%20of%20Adi%20Shankaracharya%20and%20Gandhi%20was%20subsumed%20by%20the%20divisive%2C%20insular%20nationalism%20propagated%20by%20M.S.%20Golwalkar%20and%20V.D.%20Savarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Hazlitt%20famously%20observed%20that%20the%20garb%20of%20religion%20is%20the%20best%20cloak%20for%20power.%20The%20Sangh%20parivar%E2%80%99s%20calculated%20induction%20of%20religion%20into%20the%20political%20arena%20with%20the%20clear%20intent%20of%20bestowing%20divinity%20to%20their%20politics%20has%20been%20hugely%20successful.%20A%20venom-spewing%20Yogi%20with%20a%20bulldozer%20in%20tow%20is%20the%20head%20of%20the%20largest%20state%20in%20the%20country.%20Skilfully%20using%20rituals%20to%20keep%20the%20Hindu%20ranks%20together%2C%20Valmiki%20and%20Ravidas%20pujas%20are%20conducted%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20lower%20castes.%20Today%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%2C%20despite%20mangling%20a%20great%20religious%20tradition%20of%20pluralistic%20beliefs%2C%20can%20justifiably%20claim%20to%20identify%20with%20and%20represent%20the%20collective%20will%20of%20a%20large%20section%20of%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20on%20the%20day%20that%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20torn%20down%2C%20it%20was%20palpably%20obvious%20that%20no%20power%20on%20earth%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20rebuild%20it%2C%20such%20was%20the%20visible%20might%20of%20those%20who%20engineered%20its%20destruction.%20It%20would%20be%20no%20exaggeration%20to%20state%20that%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20this%20structure%20was%20built%20the%20irresistible%20political%20juggernaut%20of%20the%20saffron%20brigade.%20The%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20which%20culminated%20in%20the%20Babri%20destruction%20resulted%20in%20a%20massive%20boost%20in%20the%20political%20fortunes%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%20and%20the%20West.%20This%20was%20reflected%20in%20the%20120%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20that%20the%20BJP%20won%20in%201991%20and%20the%20161%20seats%20with%20alliance%20partners%20that%20it%20got%20in%201996%2C%20compared%20with%20the%20measly%20two%20seats%20secured%20in%20the%201984%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Why%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20Must%20Be%20Preserved%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-the-places-of-worship-act-must-be-preserved%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20Must%20Be%20Preserved%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20decades%20later%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20hegemon%2C%20the%20undisputed%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20ruling%20in%20several%20states.%20In%20its%20wake%2C%20the%20social%20ecosystem%20is%20steaming%20with%20schismatic%20tensions%20and%20the%20rhetoric%20of%20hate.%20Gratuitous%20everyday%20cruelty%20manifested%20in%20lynchings%2C%20ghar%20wapsi%2C%20beef%20vigilantism%2C%20love%20jihad%20and%20the%20crushing%20of%20dissent%20plays%20out%20under%20the%20benign%20gaze%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20last%20bastion%20of%20our%20democracy%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%E2%80%93%20has%20bowed%20to%20majoritarian%20sentiment.%20The%20site%20of%20the%20demolished%20mosque%20has%20been%20bestowed%20to%20the%20deity%20%E2%80%9CRam%20Lalla%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20court%20has%20neither%20delivered%20justice%20nor%20adhered%20to%20the%20fundamental%20tenets%20of%20the%20law.%20Instead%2C%20%3Cem%3Eaastha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20faith%20of%20the%20majority%20community%20has%20prevailed.%20Today%20the%20country%20waits%20with%20bated%20breath%20for%20the%20grand%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024%2C%20a%20pompous%20ceremony%20that%20will%20affix%20an%20authoritative%20seal%20to%20the%20cohabitation%20of%20the%20state%20with%20the%20religion%20of%20the%20majority.%20Damn%20secularism!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20significant%20that%20this%20regime%E2%80%99s%20overwhelming%20victory%20in%20three%20of%20the%20four%20states%20that%20just%20the%20other%20day%20went%20to%20the%20polls%2C%20has%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20we%20have%20never%20been%20worse%20off%20as%20a%20nation.%20While%20the%20rich%20are%20being%20provided%20the%20wherewithal%20to%20grow%20richer%2C%20raging%20unemployment%20and%20an%20uncontrolled%20price%20rise%20have%20obliged%20the%20government%2C%20by%20its%20own%20admission%2C%20to%20provide%20free%20rations%20to%2080%20crore%20people%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years%20which%20is%20to%20be%20continued%20for%20another%20five%20years.%20The%20social%20fabric%20is%20in%20tatters%3B%20Kashmir%20is%20more%20alienated%20than%20ever%3B%20there%20is%20a%20civil%20war%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20Chinese%20are%20stomping%20all%20over%20our%20territory%20and%20we%20have%20no%20friend%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20with%20even%20the%20Maldives%20giving%20us%20the%20cold%20shoulder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20instead%20of%20concentrating%20on%20the%20real%20concerns%20of%20the%20common%20man%2C%20the%20Opposition%20has%20sought%20to%20exploit%20caste%20and%20religion%20to%20beat%20the%20BJP%20at%20its%20own%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhereas%20the%20ill%20usage%20of%20religion%20for%20political%20purposes%20has%20yielded%20massive%20dividends%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20has%20certainly%20boomeranged%20on%20the%20Opposition%20when%20it%20tries%20to%20play%20with%20soft%20Hindutva.%20(Of%20course%2C%20one%20cannot%20overlook%20the%20harmful%20impact%20of%20the%20Kamal%20Nath-Digvijay%20Singh%20duo%20for%20the%20Congress%20defeat%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20They%20ignored%20their%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20and%20thought%20that%20low%20cunning%20alone%20would%20see%20them%20through.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20face%20it.%20As%20a%20nation%2C%20we%20have%20irreversibly%20cast%20off%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20as%20a%20united%2C%20multicultural%20country%20with%20common%20goals%20and%20aspirations%2C%20a%20shared%20history%20and%20on%20a%20joint%20search%20for%20a%20better%20future%20for%20all.%20In%20its%20place%20we%20have%20Hindutva%20as%20the%20unofficial%20ideology%20of%20the%20state.%20And%20today%2C%20there%20is%20neither%20brotherhood%20nor%20love%2C%20but%20only%20manic%20hate.%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%20The%20views%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701837059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fbabri-masjid-demolition.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-babri-masjid-demolition-inalterably-changed-the-trajectory-of-indias-history%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20doctrine%20of%20Hindu%20exclusiveness%20has%20stimulated%20a%20second%20partiti