0at%205.30%20am%20and%20before%207%20am%2C%20his%20hotel%20is%20up%20and%20running%2C%20ready%20to%20welcome%20their%20customers.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20noon%2C%20we%20soak%20the%20grains%20required%20for%20the%20next%20day%E2%80%99s%20batter.%20They%20need%20to%20soak%20for%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20hours.%20By%204%20pm%2C%20we%20grind%20the%20soaked%20grains%2C%20and%20by%20late%20evening%2C%20we%20add%20salt%20to%20the%20batter%2C%20mix%20well%2C%20and%20keep%20it%20for%20fermentation.%20The%20batter%20then%20rises%20enough%20to%20make%20soft%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20morning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22in%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBabu%20Idli%20hotel%2C%20Halagur.%20Malavalli.%20Mandya.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FKarnataka%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsribasavaraju%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40sribasavaraju%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FoBMn1U7RsV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FoBMn1U7RsV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20DP%20SATISH%20(%40dp_satish)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdp_satish%2Fstatus%2F1323543096458571776%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%203%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabu%20Hotel%20is%20open%20for%20business%20between%207%20am%20and%2011%20am%20every%20day.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20exhaust%20all%20our%20batter%20in%20this%20period.%20It%20takes%20us%20the%20remaining%20day%20to%20prepare%20batter%20for%20the%20next%20day.%20We%20are%20able%20to%20wind%20up%20only%20by%208%20pm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20this%20place%20was%20an%20obscure%20eatery%20located%20in%20a%20nondescript%20hamlet%20with%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base.%20But%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20YouTubers%20and%20social%20media%20publicity%2C%20Vatsa