0not%20get%20any%20output.%20It%20has%20become%20difficult%20to%20even%20earn%20back%20the%20input%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20back%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20even%20established%20a%20water%20bank%20in%20an%20acre%20of%20land%20for%20irrigation%20purposes.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20turned%20to%20fish%20farming%20to%20utilise%20the%20water%20bank%20but%20the%20initiative%20was%20dead%20in%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFish%20farming%20did%20not%20prove%20profitable%20for%20us%20as%20it%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20input%20costs.%20If%20we%20sold%20a%20fish%20for%20Rs%20100%2C%20we%20would%20incur%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2080.%20We%20were%20only%20left%20with%20Rs%2020%20profit.%20It%20was%20very%20little%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Sanjay%20came%20across%20a%20news%20report%20that%20mentioned%20the%20profitability%20of%20oyster%20pearl%20farming.%20Motivated%20to%20try%20his%20hands%20in%20cultivating%20oysters%2C%20he%20bought%2025%2C000%20oysters%20to%20cultivate%20in%20his%20water%20bank.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20also%20roped%20in%20other%20farmer%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20collective%20investment%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20the%20group%20started%20oyster%20farming.%20And%20in%20a%20year%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F89574%2Fsanjay-gandate-pearl-farmer-gadchiroli%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerate%20an%20income%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20by%20selling%208%2C000%20pearls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farmers%20perform%20minor%20surgery%20to%20implant%20plain%20or%20designed%20pearls%20%5Ban%20artificial%20nucleus%5D%20into%20the%20tissue%20of%20a%20pearl%20oyster.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-1-1700658836-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334674%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFarmers%20perform%20minor%20surgery%20to%20implant%20plain%20or%20designed%20pearls%20%5Ban%20artificial%20nucleus%5D%20into%20the%20tissue%20of%20a%20pearl%20oyster.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20their%20success%2C%20about%2040%20farmers%20have%20joined%20Sanjay%20and%20his%20cooperative%20%E2%80%98Bless%20All%20Pearl%20Farmer%20Producer%20Company%E2%80%99.%20Together%2C%20they%20have%20planted%2050%2C000%20oysters%20and%20collaborated%20with%20companies%20like%20GKP%20Pearl%20Farm%20of%20Solapur%20and%20Namo%20Pearl%20Farm%20in%20Chandrapur%20to%20sell%20their%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cooperative%20is%20set%20to%20harvest%20its%20second%20batch%20in%20the%20upcoming%20December%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESix%20tips%20for%20beginners%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20group%20was%20able%20to%20generate%20a%20handsome%20profit%20in%20their%20very%20first%20attempt%2C%20the%20success%20rate%2C%20Sanjay%20says%2C%20was%20not%20as%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20progressive%20farmer%20travelled%20to%20Bhubaneswar%20%E2%80%94%201%2C400%20km%20f